title: Engineering Physiscs
description: Computer Science Engineering (CSE) is an academic programme that integrates the field of Computer Engineering and Computer Science. Many technical institutes in India and abroad offer UG (Undergraduate) and PG (Postgraduate) level courses in Computer Science Engineering. Students can do BTech and MTech in Computer Science Engineering from these institutes.  Students pursuing these courses get to learn about the design, implementation, and management of information systems of computer hardware and software
